{
  "stem": "24195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I turn around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, where the hell is-- why isn't he answering me, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I look at him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He's dead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somebody-- some sympathetic soul-- soul pulled him into there so he doesn't lay on the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Ah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the situation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, hours later, Russian tanks rumble up the street outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We in the basement can hear them rumbling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a little later, Russian soldiers come in the [INAUDIBLE], in the basement with the-- with their automatic weapons, looking for German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They really weren't doing any-- weren't really interested in civilians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had a-- I had to be a little bit worried, because I could have been in the German army, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they could have assumed, hey, he's a-- he's a former German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He just, you know, shed his--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uniform.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--uniform.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's now in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But otherwise, they weren't-- they were only looking for--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soldiers.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--stragglers of the German army, I mean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the next day, I could finally dare to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody tried to go out and get some fresh air.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's tanks sitting on the parkway, big T-34s.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- the man-- and the commanding officer is a very sharp-looking, in a leather outfit-- is a major or something, lieutenant in Russia-- speaks fluent German, had studied-- he was an engineer, he told me, and prior had studied, before the war, at a German university, engineering.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he-- he was the first one to tell us what the outlook was going to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, don't expect the Americans to come here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, this is the [? outer. ?] That was decided that we get, the Russians get, Berlin, get to keep Berlin, which was later changed, so you know, they had the four zones.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
